- Later, `copy_to_user` uses `minsz` (the fixed size of the struct up to `offset`).
- **But**: There is a **critical section** where `caps.size` is used:
```c
if (caps.size) {
    info.flags |= VFIO_REGION_INFO_FLAG_CAPS;
    if (info.argsz < sizeof(info) + caps.size) {
        info.argsz = sizeof(info) + caps.size;
        info.cap_offset = 0;
    } else {
