### 5. `VFIO_DEVICE_RESET`
- No `argsz` involved.
- ✅ Safe.

---

### 6. `VFIO_DEVICE_GET_PCI_HOT_RESET_INFO`
```c
if (copy_from_user(&hdr, (void __user *)arg, minsz))
    return -EFAULT;

if (hdr.argsz < minsz)
